# URL Shortener
URL Shortener is an application that allows users to shorten long URLs. The app is built using React.js, Node.js, and MongoDB.

## Features

User authentication

URL shortening and redirection

View short URL statistics

Admin dashboard to manage URLs and users

## Installation

Clone the repository: git clone https://github.com/your-username/url-shortener.git

Install dependencies for both client and server: npm install

Set up environment variables:

Create a .env file in the root directory of the server

Add the following environment variables:

Replace your-mongodb-uri with the MongoDB URI for your database, and your-secret-key with a secret key for your app

Start the app: npm run dev

